  <tr>
    <td colspan="3" width="100%"><p align="center">
    <font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="2">A huge animal, the wooly mammoth can easily crush a level 20 solo.  They have no special abilities, but they are so strong that they really don't need any.  They give tusks for loot, although I am not sure what size tusks.</font></td>
  </tr>
