		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			The level range of these beasties are way off.  As a 19th level wizard, practically every single one of these will resist my spells completely (not a little bit of damage--I mean 100% resist).  Given that this only happens when the target is 6 or more levels above a wizard, this would put them at at least 25.  My 27th level shaman friend cons these as blue--so most of the mammoths appear to be between 25-26 level.  There was one &quot;weaker&quot; mammoth which I was able to help bring down--I suspect the correct range for these are between 24 - 26 level.  Fortunately, I was SoWed so I was able to get my scrawny Erudite butt outta there in a hurry...
			</font>
	
