			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			These are great for level 20 or higher magicians to hunt because the tusks fit inside the dimensional pockets that magicians can summon. That will also render them weightless. Which means that it is possible for a magician to fill up with 32 of these if he carries a dimensional pocket in each o his inventory slots. 32 * 10 = 320pp. Of course, one would probably never reach 32 but even half that is a lot of money.
